OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779019866
OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,FWes Streeting has confirmed he will
OL,7,Fstand in any Labour leadership race to
OL,8,Freplace Prime Minister Keir Starmer.
OL,10,F"We need a proper contest with the
OL,11,Fbest candidates in the field, and I'll
OL,12,Fbe standing," the former health
OL,13,Fsecretary said as he finished his
OL,14,Fspeech at the Progress conference in
OL,15,FLondon on Saturday.
OL,17,FAsked if he had 81 MPs to back him to
OL,18,Fstand, Streeting told reporters he had
OL,19,Fsupport in the parliamentary party and
OL,20,Fdenied he was causing division within
OL,21,FLabour with his leadership bid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
