PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779019866
OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,F"We could have rushed straight into a
OL,7,Fleadership contest knowing that not
OL,8,Fall of the candidates would be on the
OL,9,Fpitch, that Andy Burnham was about to
OL,10,Fstand in a by-election," Streeting
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,F"If we had rushed ahead without giving
OL,14,FAndy a chance to stand, the new
OL,15,Fleader, whether it was me or anyone
OL,16,Felse, would lack the legitimacy. And
OL,17,Fso we would end up extending
OL,18,Finstability and uncertainty.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
