OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,F"That might have been the self
OL,12,Finterested thing to do for candidates
OL,13,Fwho are in parliament presently, but
OL,14,Fit wasn't in the parties interests and
OL,15,Fwasn't in the national interest.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
