OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779019866
OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,F"If you think you're good enough to do
OL,7,Fthe top job, if you think you've got
OL,8,Fthe right ideas for the country, you
OL,9,Fshould be prepared to put them
OL,10,Fforward, test them against other
OL,11,Fcompetitors and win an election. And
OL,12,Fthat was a choice that I made."
OL,14,FIn his speech, Streeting warned that
OL,15,FLabour will be "the handmaidens of
OL,16,FNigel Farage and the breakup of the
OL,17,FUnited Kingdom" unless it changes
OL,18,Fcourse.
OL,26,@wD@POUyD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
