OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,FDescribing Reform UK and Farage as the
OL,7,Fparty's biggest opposition, Streeting
OL,8,Fused his speech to call for Labour to
OL,9,Fbe bolder in confronting racism and
OL,10,Fsaid Britain should rejoin the EU.
OL,12,F"English nationalism is a threat to
OL,13,Fthe values and ideals that have made
OL,14,Fthis country great," he said.
OL,16,F"Progressives understand this threat
OL,17,Fbut they are increasingly losing faith
OL,18,Fthat the Labour Party is capable of
OL,19,Frising to the challenge."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
