CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779019866
OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,F"Where we need vision, we have a
OL,7,Fvacuum. Where we need direction, we
OL,8,Fhave drift," he wrote.
OL,10,FIn response to Streeting's letter,
OL,11,FStarmer wrote back praising his work
OL,12,Fand pointing to figures published this
OL,13,Fweek showing NHS waiting times had
OL,14,Fbeen cut dramatically.
OL,16,FEarlier on Saturday, Greater
OL,17,FManchester Mayor Andy Burnham was
OL,18,Fcleared to run in the Makerfield by-
OL,19,Felection by the Labour Party's ruling
OL,20,Fbody, paving his way to mount a
OL,21,Fleadership challenge to Starmer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
