OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1779019866
OL,3,CWes Streeting confirms he will stand
OL,4,Cin Labour leadership race
OL,6,FCurrent MP, Josh Simons, announced on
OL,7,FThursday he would stand down from his
OL,8,Frole to make way for Burnham.
OL,10,F"Labour's ruling body, the National
OL,11,FExecutive Committee, has today given
OL,12,Fpermission to Andy Burnham to stand in
OL,13,Fthe candidate selection process in the
OL,14,Fforthcoming by-election for the
OL,15,FMakerfield constituency," a Labour
OL,16,FParty spokesperson said.
